{"title":"边民大联欢之夜","authors":["王海"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"边民大联欢之夜\t王海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是黑漆漆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩灯和歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变了夜的模样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹林边乐声悠扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞池里起伏着欢乐的波浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只剩下一个中年男子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤伶伶坐在一旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘走来向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他鞠躬他连忙站起来，带着为难的笑容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说：“我过去很爱跳舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞起来，像一阵旋风”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他沉痛地掀起裤脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出木制的腿来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的真腿已经沉没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在太平洋里在苦难的战争年代……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了亚非和全世界爱跳舞的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别再失去宝贵的腿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跛子迈着坚定的充满信心的步伐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从千里外赶来参加边民联欢大会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是黑漆漆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩灯和歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变了夜的模样"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}